    "/api/events": {
      "post": {
        "summary": "Add Event",
        "description": "New in this change: record an event and recompute trending. The recompute sorts the\nentire unbounded in-memory log on every write, so per-request work grows with how much\ntraffic the test has already sent. Fine when serial or short; under load p95 creeps up.",
